      "name": "Five-point bench hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against in-vitro measurements at five flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 38%; prediction consistently over-estimates hemolysis. Validation activities conducted at conditions representative of COU but absolute agreement insufficient for MRL 5 acceptance."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/validation/monte-carlo-uq-result",
