      "description": "1500-sample Monte Carlo propagation of inlet velocity, fluid viscosity, and power-law hemolysis model coefficients through the CFD surrogate. 95th-percentile hemolysis index exceeds clinical threshold at two of five operating points, confirming unacceptable predictive uncertainty at MRL 5."
    }
  ],
